 ↞---------------|ABILITIES|---------------↠

  Berserk:

    Whenever this Pokémon takes 
  damage from a move that causes 
  its HP to drop below 50%, its 
  Special Attack rises by one stage.

  Sap-sipper:

    Whenever a grass-type move 
  hits this Pokémon, its Attack 
  rises one stage, negating any 
  other effect on it.

  Cloud-nine:

    While this Pokémon is in battle, 
  weather can still be in play, 
  but will not have any of its 
  effects.

  This ability functions identically 
  to air lock.


